**expanded-text-ad**

This is the ad simplest ad on Google Ads.

<%= image_tag "creatives/goog_expanded_text.png",
  class: 'goog creative expanded-text' %>

**type:** `expanded_text_ad`.
<br>
**spec:** These are the keys you have to provide.

- `headline_part1` (string): first line of the title.
- `headline_part2` (string): second line of the title.
- `description` (string): description shown in the ad.
- `link (string)`: where are users redirected to.
